lead_paragraph: Nice returned to the top of Ligue 1 as Younes Belhanda's early goal downed Guingamp 1-0 away on Wednesday while Paris St Germain moved above AS Monaco into second with a 2-0 home win over Angers.

headline.print_headline: Nice Regain Top Spot, PSG Overtake Monaco
